        <num>CC 2988</num>
        <heading>2988.  Applicability of the rules of mandate</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2988.  Applicability of the rules of mandate
A procuration is subject to the rules governing mandate to the extent that the application of those rules is compatible with the nature of the procuration.</p>
        </content>
